Type: Package
Package: modelsummary
Title: Create Beautiful, Customisable, Publication-Ready Summary Tables for
    Statistical Models
Description: Create beautiful, customisable, publication-ready summary tables
    for statistical models. `modelsummary` leverages the power of the `gt` and `broom`
    packages. It can produce tables in html, rtf, and LaTeX formats
    (text/markdown/ascii tables coming soon).
Version: 0.1.0
